parameters:
Oh--! If it isn't Karin-san! Have you been well? It's been a
while!

You cut your hair, didn't you? I almost didn't recognize you
for a moment...

Heh heh! I look pretty handsome with my hair and beard
shaved off, right? Before I was exiled, I was known as the
stylish Kisanosuke.

I heard a fatty tuna specialty shop had opened, but to think
it was your shop, Kisanosuke-san? I was surprised...

Ha ha ha! Didn't I tell you when we were living on the
island? If I could escape from the island, I wanted to make
fatty tuna popular in Edo--I used the money I earned from
loading cargo as capital to rent an empty house and open the
shop. And then it became more popular than I could have ever
imagined

That's great. You were able to spread the deliciousness of
fatty tuna to the people of Edo.

Yeah. Since we're reunited, Karin-san, please have some
fatty tuna. Of course, there's no charge. Come on, come
on--!
Mmm, delicious...\I[15]This melting texture is irresistible

Heh heh! I'm glad to see you enjoying it. Being able to open
the shop of my dreams in Edo, it's really all thanks to you,
Karin-san. Kachou-san is in the back room. Feel free to call
out to her.
Yes! Thank you for the meal!

\c[17]--Karin's technique power maximum value has increased by
10\c[0]

I'm so happy that the shop is thriving I want to keep this
life going forever. Karin-san, you should live happily too.

It's been a while, Kachou-san. Have you been well? Did you
change your hairstyle?

Yes. At first, I was hiding because I thought the officials
might catch me, but it seems safe now, so I've started
living in this tenement house in Ueno.

I'm glad to see your shop is thriving I was surprised to
find out that Kisanosuke-san is running a shop.

Hehe. I never imagined that from eating Toro together on
Mujou Island, a shop would come to be. Kisanosuke-san is
very motivated, and we're very grateful that the number of
customers increases day by day.
It's all thanks to you, Karin-san. Really, truly, thank you.

If you'd like, please take this with you. It's a hairpin I
made with the tropical flowers of Mujou Island.
Wow! Thank you so much, Kachou-san I will cherish it!

This tenement is full of flowers, isn't it? I brought seeds
of tropical flowers. They sell for quite a high price in
Edo, so I'm glad I secretly brought them with me.

Kisanosuke-san is also kind to us, and we're living very
happily as a family of three. Thank you, Karin-san.

I never knew fatty tuna could be this delicious This place
is as good as the rumors say.

I'm totally hooked on fatty tuna. I've been coming here to
eat it every day.

This is my first time at a fatty tuna specialty shop. It's
tastier than I expected, I'm surprised.

This shop didn't have many customers when it first opened,
but it quickly became popular due to its good reputation.
I'm in line waiting right now.

Yummy, yummy! It's cheap, delicious, and just the best!
Boss, another plate of fatty tuna, please!
